hobn zey gehat a paruk-makherstve

00:15:00.160 --> 00:15:02.047
mit zayn bruder, ye?

00:15:01.666 --> 00:15:06.352
ye.

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:11.180
vu hot ir zikh opgeshribn? in shul ir hot gehat a khupe?

00:15:11.180 --> 00:15:15.020
i mir hobn zikh opgeshribn i gemakht a khupe oykh.

00:15:15.020 --> 00:15:16.760
gemakht a khupe.

00:15:15.710 --> 00:15:16.547
ye

00:15:16.760 --> 00:15:17.840
ye.

00:15:17.840 --> 00:15:20.960
in shul ir hot dos gekent makhn, ye?

00:15:20.960 --> 00:15:21.620
ha?

00:15:21.620 --> 00:15:25.202
un ir gedenkt vi es hot zikh do- vi hot dos oysge-

00:15:23.700 --> 00:15:25.480
ikh hob zikh gedreyt!

00:15:25.480 --> 00:15:29.266
vi iz, hot dos oysgezen?

00:15:26.300 --> 00:15:29.060
kh'hob zikh fardreyt di kop!

00:15:29.266 --> 00:15:31.640
vi hot dos oysgezen, gedenkt ir?

00:15:31.640 --> 00:15:32.920
far vos nit?

00:15:32.920 --> 00:15:34.860
ir kent dertseyln?

00:15:34.860 --> 00:15:38.380
oy, a gezunt aykh in kop, ir halt mikh oyf nokh lang?

00:15:38.380 --> 00:15:40.500
neyn, nit lang.

00:15:40.500 --> 00:15:42.820
vos ken ikh dertseyln?

00:15:42.820 --> 00:15:45.840
m'hot avekgeshtelt a a dekhl aza

00:15:45.840 --> 00:15:48.480
mit fir fleklekh

00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:51.040
un di.

00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:54.800
s'iz geven unterfirer. veyst ir vos dos iz?

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:57.240
dertseylt vos dos iz.

00:15:57.240 --> 00:15:59.120
unterfirer.

00:15:59.120 --> 00:16:03.040
UNK YA SEYCHAS PLOKHA MNYE DELAT'SYA

00:16:03.040 --> 00:16:06.240
dertseylt vos iz dos unterfirer bite.

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:07.920
vos iz unterfirer?

00:16:07.920 --> 00:16:08.680
ye.

00:16:08.680 --> 00:16:11.280
nu dos iz vi SVIDETEL'NE.

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:14.180
vi eydes.

00:16:14.180 --> 00:16:14.740
ha?

00:16:14.740 --> 00:16:16.220
vi eydes.

00:16:16.220 --> 00:16:17.140
ye.

00:16:18.535 --> 00:16:19.498
ye, ye.

00:16:18.680 --> 00:16:21.820
un ver iz geven di unterfirer?

00:16:21.820 --> 00:16:29.700
Lurye.

00:16:29.700 --> 00:16:33.760
ver iz nokh dortn geven?

00:16:33.760 --> 00:16:40.940
dos gedenk ikh shoyn gornit,. finf un fuftsik, vifl? finf un fuftsik yor tsurik.

00:16:40.940 --> 00:16:44.540
dos iz geven in fertsikstn tsu in eyn un fertsikstn yor?

00:16:44.540 --> 00:16:48.960
dos iz geven zeks monat far di krig.

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:51.720
s'iz geven vinter tsu zumer?

00:16:51.720 --> 00:16:53.620
s'iz geven in osyen.

00:16:57.780 --> 00:17:01.400
in herbst.

00:17:01.400 --> 00:17:05.560
nu, un vi lang iz dos alts geven, di khupe un alts?

00:17:05.560 --> 00:17:09.913
dos iz a dire gevezn. dra-

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:09.860
nu?

00:17:09.860 --> 00:17:13.837
un di khasene vi iz geven? vu iz zi geven?

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:17.880
nu, a oreme khasene, vi iz geven? vi hot gekent zayn?

00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:20.840
nit geven keyn farmeglekhe.

00:17:20.840 --> 00:17:25.040
un fun di yidishe gemeynde hot aykh ver nit iz geholfn?

00:17:25.040 --> 00:17:27.960
ir zayt geven fun a oreme mishpokhe?

00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:35.480
keyner nit. keyner nit. vi mir hobn gekent azoy hobn mir gemakht.

00:17:35.480 --> 00:17:40.140
nu un dernokh vos iz geven nokh di khasene?

00:17:40.140 --> 00:17:43.040
m'hot gelebt.

00:17:43.040 --> 00:17:45.920
⟨gekumen⟩ fun lager

00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:47.100
neyn.

00:17:47.100 --> 00:17:48.529
⟨shoyn⟩ nokh nit?

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:51.020
ye, s'iz nokh nit.

00:17:51.020 --> 00:17:58.780
nu, ot itster vayter vi es hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome kent ir dertseyln shoyn, oyb ir hot nit vos dertseyln biz dos.

00:17:58.780 --> 00:18:04.060
nu, s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome, hobn mir, hobn mir zikh, geven oysgebahaltn.

00:18:04.060 --> 00:18:09.060
ir gedenkt dem tog vi es h-, zi hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome?

00:18:09.060 --> 00:18:10.385
dem tog.

00:18:10.385 --> 00:18:11.300
neyn.

00:18:11.300 --> 00:18:12.180
un v-

00:18:11.594 --> 00:18:14.820
m'iz geven azoy tserudert az ikh gedenk gornit.

00:18:14.820 --> 00:18:18.320
un vi hot ir zikh dervust az se hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome?

00:18:18.320 --> 00:18:20.740
m'hot ongehoybn bombardirn.

00:18:20.932 --> 00:18:21.540
Kovne.

00:18:21.340 --> 00:18:24.640
mir zaynen gelegn in a podval.

00:18:24.640 --> 00:18:27.340
nu, ongehoybn bom- bombardirn.

00:18:27.340 --> 00:18:32.140
un arayn di daytshn, zaynen mir shoyn aroysgekrokhn. vos zoln mir shoyn lign dortn?

00:18:32.140 --> 00:18:36.480
un vu zayt ir geven in podval? in keler?

00:18:36.480 --> 00:18:41.260
Ashkenazi, oyf Yatkever gas. zaynen mir gelegn in keler.

00:18:41.260 --> 00:18:43.800
nokh a fule zaynen mir gelegn.

00:18:43.800 --> 00:18:45.912
un ver iz nokh geven mit aykh?

00:18:45.720 --> 00:18:50.400
geven nokh yidn ver, ikh hob zey nit gekent ver zey zaynen geven.

00:18:50.400 --> 00:18:55.364
un vu iz geven ayer mishpokhe, di shvester, di brider, veyst ir nit?

00:18:54.400 --> 00:18:57.600
nu, tsevorfn zaynen mir gevezn.

00:18:57.600 --> 00:18:58.800
es zaynen geven mit di

00:18:58.800 --> 00:19:08.140
mit di kinder, mit di mener, un mir zaynen vider geven andersh. ikh bin geven mit mayn man.

00:19:08.140 --> 00:19:09.820
makht dos oyf gikh.

00:19:09.820 --> 00:19:14.340
nu, un vi di daytshn, ven zaynen zey arayn?

00:19:14.340 --> 00:19:15.400
ven zaynen zey arayn?

00:19:14.379 --> 00:19:14.786
durkh

00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:18.940
durkh vifl teg?

00:19:18.940 --> 00:19:24.280
mir dukht a in a tog arum mir dakht zikh mir.

00:19:24.280 --> 00:19:28.380
m'hot ongehoybn bombardirn, un zey zaynen arayn. m'hot zey n-

00:19:28.380 --> 00:19:31.780
s'iz shoyn gevezn a iberkerenish

00:19:31.780 --> 00:19:34.500
fun di litviner.

00:19:34.500 --> 00:19:37.520
m'hot shoyn gehat moyre tsu geyn in gas.

00:19:37.520 --> 00:19:40.440
ikh hob oykh gekrogn a klap in kop.

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:43.200
nu vi alt bin ikh gevezn, gegangen

00:19:43.200 --> 00:19:47.880
fun di mamen in shtub, hot mir a patsh geton a kristin ibern kop.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:50.020
un ven iz dos geven shoyn?

00:19:50.020 --> 00:19:52.175
az di daytshn zaynen shoyn geven?

00:19:51.600 --> 00:19:53.760
az di daytshn zaynen gevezn.

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:59.820
un s'iz geven, dos iz geven zumer tsu s'iz geven vinter, ir gedenkt?

00:19:59.820 --> 00:20:03.980
nu, s'iz zumer in der, der tsayt epes.

00:20:03.980 --> 00:20:06.320
in der tsayt dakht zikh.

00:20:06.320 --> 00:20:11.480
vos hot ir gegesn? vu hot ir gekrogn esn in ot aza min shvere tsayt?

00:20:11.480 --> 00:20:13.760
vu hot men gekrogn?

00:20:13.760 --> 00:20:18.960
m'hot gegebn farfoylte bulbes un m'hot gemakht fun dem

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:21.720
m'hot gemakht.

00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:26.060
kuglen fun sholekhts.

00:20:26.060 --> 00:20:29.811
V OBSHCHEM far derfar iz dokh a geto hot zikh ongerufn.

00:20:29.580 --> 00:20:33.320
un ven iz geven, ven hot men aykh farmakht in geto?

00:20:33.320 --> 00:20:38.700
ven hot undz farmakht? m'hot geheysn alemen aroysgeyn fun di dires in

00:20:38.700 --> 00:20:42.940
in sh- fun shtot, un m'hot geheysn

00:20:42.940 --> 00:20:44.480
geyn in geto.

00:20:44.480 --> 00:20:50.200
iz ver es hot gevelt, hot zikh frier bazorgt.

00:20:50.200 --> 00:20:55.600
un ver es hot, ot mir hobn gelebt in dortn, oyf KRISCIUKAICIO.

00:20:55.600 --> 00:21:00.100
m'iz geblibn lebn in di zelbe dire.

00:21:00.100 --> 00:21:01.620
ir farshteyt?

00:21:01.620 --> 00:21:06.600
lebn mit undz hobn gelebt di shvester shoyn.

00:21:06.600 --> 00:21:08.140
ayer shvester?

00:21:08.140 --> 00:21:12.520
ye, shvester. tsvey shvester mit di kinder.

00:21:12.520 --> 00:21:14.280
gelebt.

00:21:14.280 --> 00:21:18.621
un di iberike fun ayere mishpokhe-mitglider?

00:21:17.580 --> 00:21:22.280
eyner iz gegange- geforn oyf Utyan.

00:21:22.280 --> 00:21:24.120
iz er kontik

00:21:24.120 --> 00:21:27.640
vu er iz ahingekumen veys ikh nit.

00:21:27.640 --> 00:21:32.860
er iz, vayzt oys, hot men im oyfn d-, unter di vegns gepatert.

00:21:32.860 --> 00:21:37.200
im un a froy mit tsvey kinder.

00:21:37.200 --> 00:21:41.280
dos iz geven velkher ayer bruder?

00:21:37.640 --> 00:21:38.461
az

00:21:41.280 --> 00:21:48.200
Yosl.

00:21:48.860 --> 00:21:51.121
di iberike brider ayere?

00:21:50.960 --> 00:21:54.400
eyner iz gevezn in geto.

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:55.980
velkher?

00:21:55.980 --> 00:21:59.840
Khemtshik.

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:02.540
un Kalmen iz oykh geven in geto.

00:22:02.540 --> 00:22:08.160
nor er hot zikh oysgebahaltn in la- in, aroysgeshikt in Daytshland

00:22:08.160 --> 00:22:14.180
hot men im nit, vayl er hot zikh gehat oysgebahaltn.

00:22:14.180 --> 00:22:17.200
un zeyere kinder vu zaynen geven?

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:20.260
eyner hot keyn kinder nit gehat.

00:22:20.260 --> 00:22:24.280
der tsveyter iz, hot gehat a krankn kind.

00:22:24.280 --> 00:22:27.700
mir dukht az di daytshn zaynen arayn, hobn zey im tsug-

00:22:27.700 --> 00:22:32.820
tsuzamen genumen mit di kinder mit im tsuzamen.

00:22:32.820 --> 00:22:36.740
nu, un ot dan hot men undz geshikt oyf der arbet

00:22:36.740 --> 00:22:38.532
vu hot ir gearbet?

00:22:38.080 --> 00:22:41.020
in PALEMON.

00:22:41.020 --> 00:22:48.380
bay tsigl.

00:22:48.380 --> 00:22:51.480
vi hot men aykh getribn oyf der arbet?

00:22:51.480 --> 00:22:52.140
ah?

00:22:52.140 --> 00:22:54.316
vi hot men aykh getribn oyf der arbet?

00:22:54.000 --> 00:23:00.100
nu, nit vayt fun vu mir zaynen gevezn. s'iz geven, m'hot gemakht a fabrik iz dort geven

00:23:00.100 --> 00:23:01.600
fun tsigl.

00:23:01.600 --> 00:23:03.440
flegt men oysarbetn

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:08.340
un mir flegn onlad-, firn mit di vagonetkes.

00:23:08.340 --> 00:23:11.560
un vu hot ir gefirt?

00:23:11.560 --> 00:23:17.960
gefirt in, avekley- oystsuleygn zey oyf a, oyf an ort avekleygn.

00:23:17.960 --> 00:23:23.160
un vifl hot ir ot azoy gearbet sho in tog?

00:23:23.160 --> 00:23:26.560
an arbets-tog.

00:23:26.560 --> 00:23:29.320
esn vos hot, hot men aykh gegebn?

00:23:29.320 --> 00:23:34.060
ye, m'hot gegebn esn. ferdn-fleysh

00:23:34.060 --> 00:23:39.300
m'hot gegebn. m'hot zikh ongegesn gut.

00:23:39.300 --> 00:23:40.920
un zakhn?

00:23:40.920 --> 00:23:41.640
ah?

00:23:41.640 --> 00:23:44.689
vu hot ir genumen zakhn oyf ot aza min arbet?

00:23:43.800 --> 00:23:47.580
zakhn? dos vos mir hobn gehat hobn mir

00:23:47.580 --> 00:23:49.660
nu, k- keyn, keyn f-

00:23:49.660 --> 00:23:52.680
keyn mashin mit zakhn hobn mir nit gekent firn.

00:23:52.680 --> 00:23:58.140
dos vos mir hobn gehat oyf zikh, un nokh epes a

00:23:58.140 --> 00:24:01.840
azoy keyn, hobn mir ibergelozn.

00:24:01.840 --> 00:24:04.720
un, nu, ibergelozn di tir ofn

00:24:04.720 --> 00:24:07.800
un azoy iz geblibn. tseshlept gevorn.

00:24:07.800 --> 00:24:11.340
ayer man vos hot geton in geto?

00:24:11.340 --> 00:24:13.800
vos hot er geton in geto?

00:24:13.800 --> 00:24:18.200
er fleg geyn oyfn flug-plats. dos iz oyfn aerodrom.

00:24:18.200 --> 00:24:21.840
arbetn. fleg ikh oykh geyn dortn.

00:24:21.840 --> 00:24:24.380
mir flegt men oykh nemen.

00:24:24.380 --> 00:24:27.660
un vos hot er dortn geton?

00:24:27.660 --> 00:24:29.980
grobn gre-

00:24:29.980 --> 00:24:31.200
griber.

00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:34.480
griber, ye.

00:24:34.480 --> 00:24:37.760
vi flegt men aykh batsoln far ot aza min arbet?

00:24:37.540 --> 00:24:44.800
batsoln? mit klep!

00:24:44.800 --> 00:24:47.200
dernokh

00:24:47.200 --> 00:24:50.100
nokh der arbet in geto

00:24:50.100 --> 00:24:52.080
nokh der arbet in geto?

00:24:52.182 --> 00:24:54.000
ye.

00:24:54.000 --> 00:24:55.202
iz vos?

00:24:54.459 --> 00:24:56.405
vi hot ir gelebt?

00:24:56.520 --> 00:24:58.477
nu, vi hot men gekent lebn?

00:24:57.380 --> 00:25:01.120
ir hot gehat shkheynim? velkhe? vemenen?

00:25:02.740 --> 00:25:05.840
s'hot gelebt oyfn hoyf in di moy-

00:25:05.840 --> 00:25:08.380
hot gelebt zayn bruder

00:25:08.380 --> 00:25:12.020
mit a vayb, mit kinder.

00:25:12.020 --> 00:25:16.760
s'hot gelebt nokh, nor ikh gedenk di familyes zeyere?

00:25:16.760 --> 00:25:19.800
s'hobn gelebt nokh yidn dortn

00:25:19.800 --> 00:25:21.520
in a moyer.

00:25:21.520 --> 00:25:24.000
un ayere shvesters vu?

00:25:24.000 --> 00:25:26.021
zaynen geven vayt fun aykh?

00:25:25.780 --> 00:25:31.560
neyn. gelebt mit undz tsuzamen.

00:25:31.560 --> 00:25:37.040
ver nit iz hot aykh geholfn mit aza min lebn?

00:25:37.040 --> 00:25:41.480
ver hot gekent helfn? yeder eyner vos hot gehat

00:25:41.480 --> 00:25:45.000
me flegt fo- f- avekshikn in a kleyn shtetl

00:25:45.000 --> 00:25:48.840
arbetn flegt men mitnemen di zakhn

00:25:48.840 --> 00:25:52.700
un me flegt oysbaytn oyfn esn.

00:25:52.700 --> 00:25:56.740
bulves, broyt.

00:25:56.740 --> 00:26:01.860
nokh, dortn,⟨a shal⟩, ikh veys vos me flegt oysbaytn.

00:26:01.860 --> 00:26:05.260
un vi hot men dos arayngetrogn dernokh in geto?

00:26:05.260 --> 00:26:09.580
ot dos iz geven shver. a mol flegt men dos

00:26:09.580 --> 00:26:12.300
flegt men rizikirn

00:26:12.300 --> 00:26:16.380
un me flegt trogn, un me flegt tsunemen

00:26:16.380 --> 00:26:18.020
baym toyer

00:26:18.020 --> 00:26:22.940
SMOTRYA vos far a postns es flegn shteyn fun di daytshn.

00:26:22.940 --> 00:26:27.980
un der pekl iz gevorn oys.

00:26:27.980 --> 00:26:32.900
in geto hot ir, kinder hobn zikh gekent bay aykh lernen?

00:26:32.900 --> 00:26:34.905
kleyne kinder.

00:26:33.135 --> 00:26:37.360
neyn, neyn, neyn.

00:26:37.360 --> 00:26:42.820
keyn klasn iz nit geven.

00:26:42.820 --> 00:26:46.540
in yudnrat hot ir zikh gevendet ven nit iz?

00:26:46.540 --> 00:26:47.220
vos?

00:26:47.220 --> 00:26:50.320
in yudnrat hot ir zikh gevendet ven nit iz?

00:26:50.320 --> 00:26:51.520
avu avu?

00:26:50.986 --> 00:26:53.600
hilf far di kinder,

00:26:53.600 --> 00:26:55.060
vos nit iz,

00:26:55.060 --> 00:26:57.920
aykh iz oysgekumen zikh vendn?

00:26:57.920 --> 00:26:59.240
neyn.

00:26:59.240 --> 00:27:01.880
vos iz do tsu vendn geven? tsu vemen?

00:27:01.880 --> 00:27:03.820
un vinter?

00:27:03.820 --> 00:27:11.000
vinter? flegn mir geyn oyf der arbet un frirn.

